WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.000
20.03.2003 Nirmal Dham, Delhi (India )

00:00:05.375 --> 00:00:07.083
Today everybody is

00:00:07.375 --> 00:00:10.291
trying to talk to you in English language

00:00:10.667 --> 00:00:16.834
because, I think, they feel the majority of you are

00:00:18.125 --> 00:00:20.250
speaking English.

00:00:24.458 --> 00:00:33.458
I wish I could tell you something new about life.

00:00:37.959 --> 00:00:40.125
Life goes on moving.

00:00:40.166 --> 00:00:44.166
Whether you are eighty or ninety, makes no difference.

00:00:47.208 --> 00:00:48.834
Only thing is

00:00:52.291 --> 00:00:54.583
how much you have

00:00:54.875 --> 00:00:59.291
used the light that you have got it in Sahaja Yoga.

00:01:02.667 --> 00:01:06.000
All of you are now enlightened in Sahaja Yoga,

00:01:07.458 --> 00:01:09.166
all your Kundalinis are up

00:01:09.542 --> 00:01:12.166
and I think you know most of it.

00:01:12.542 --> 00:01:16.667
But despite that it's important

00:01:17.125 --> 00:01:19.542
how much time you devote

00:01:20.834 --> 00:01:23.834
for the emancipation of human beings,

00:01:24.208 --> 00:01:26.959
for helping them to come out

00:01:27.041 --> 00:01:31.959
instead of criticizing them, instead of condemning them.

00:01:32.041 --> 00:01:37.542
Your duty is to put them on a higher pedestal,

00:01:37.959 --> 00:01:40.125
so they respect themselves and

00:01:40.166 --> 00:01:42.041
respect their Self Realization.

00:01:42.458 --> 00:01:45.041
Is very important because

00:01:45.458 --> 00:01:49.291
I met many Sahaja Yogis to begin with

00:01:49.709 --> 00:01:54.125
who were very much critical of their colleagues and

00:01:54.458 --> 00:01:55.959
all other things.

00:01:56.041 --> 00:01:59.542
But since they have got Realization

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:02.542
they think It's a matter of duty for them.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:05.834
That is they should attend

00:02:06.208 --> 00:02:12.125
to the emancipation of human beings.

00:02:12.166 --> 00:02:15.542
Then there won't be any problem of any kind.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:21.166
No political problem, no economic problem, nothing of the kind.

00:02:21.542 --> 00:02:26.208
All these problems are created by mind

00:02:26.333 --> 00:02:30.709
which is not yet fully developed I should say,

00:02:31.125 --> 00:02:35.125
and once it is developed, you are not bothered,

00:02:35.166 --> 00:02:38.291
you are bothered about others,

00:02:38.333 --> 00:02:42.000
you are bothered about emancipation of others.

00:02:42.041 --> 00:02:45.709
It's automatic. I don't have to say that.

00:02:46.125 --> 00:02:48.625
But you have seen in your lives

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:52.125
how your attitudes have changed towards life

00:02:52.166 --> 00:02:55.709
and that is what is more important than anything else.

00:02:57.041 --> 00:03:01.792
Some of you are very successful people in politics,

00:03:02.041 --> 00:03:04.959
in business, in this and that.

00:03:05.458 --> 00:03:11.041
But you are not satisfied till you give Realization to people

00:03:11.709 --> 00:03:15.333
- till you make them perfect like yourself.

00:03:15.709 --> 00:03:20.041
So very happy to see so many people being

00:03:20.458 --> 00:03:22.041
helped by Sahaja Yoga.

00:03:22.458 --> 00:03:26.625
I never expected that in My life time only I'll see this.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:33.000
It is worked out, worked out so wonderfully, I am really amazed

00:03:33.041 --> 00:03:36.041
how things grew so fast

00:03:36.458 --> 00:03:39.917
and how it has grown into so many countries,

00:03:40.208 --> 00:03:44.000
into the so many people's heart

00:03:44.333 --> 00:03:48.041
and how they have taken to Sahaja Yoga.

00:03:48.041 --> 00:03:52.625
They are working not only in their own country but also outside.

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:57.166
After all I can't go every where now.

00:03:57.166 --> 00:04:01.166
But despite that Sahaja Yoga is spreading

00:04:01.333 --> 00:04:06.709
which is such a great thing for Me. So satisfying.

00:04:07.166 --> 00:04:10.041
You have no idea when I hear

00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:12.041
that Sahaja Yoga  has gone

00:04:12.375 --> 00:04:15.041
to this country and gone to that country.

00:04:15.500 --> 00:04:19.041
Practically they say in forty-three countries

00:04:19.500 --> 00:04:23.083
Sahaja Yoga is settled down in a very large way,

00:04:23.417 --> 00:04:28.792
and in a smaller way may be it is in many more.

00:04:29.083 --> 00:04:32.875
But to hear this also

00:04:33.208 --> 00:04:37.291
I never expected that it would work that fast.

00:04:37.709 --> 00:04:39.250
It's all thanks to you,

00:04:39.542 --> 00:04:44.709
to you Sahaja Yogis, who has achieved this miracle.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:49.917
I am thankful to you all from India and abroad,

00:04:50.208 --> 00:04:58.917
those who have taken up the flag of emancipation

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:04.208
and are moving forward instead of criticizing,

00:05:04.500 --> 00:05:07.792
instead of degrading some people

00:05:08.291 --> 00:05:10.583
- very easy to do that.

00:05:11.166 --> 00:05:13.959
But what about you, yourself,

00:05:14.291 --> 00:05:19.875
rising above all that and make others rise also.

00:05:20.125 --> 00:05:22.208
We can change the whole world,

00:05:22.625 --> 00:05:28.875
and you start understanding the problems of the world

00:05:29.291 --> 00:05:34.500
and you can get rid of them with your Kundalini awakening.

00:05:34.875 --> 00:05:37.875
Such a great thing is this Kundalini, I tell you,

00:05:38.291 --> 00:05:44.041
that it makes human beings something superlative,

00:05:44.125 --> 00:05:48.625
is all described as saints and this and that.

00:05:49.041 --> 00:05:53.875
But a Sahaja Yogi has a greater power

00:05:54.291 --> 00:05:58.125
and the greater power is that he can make other Sahaja Yogi,

00:05:58.500 --> 00:06:01.291
he can give Realizations to others.

00:06:01.375 --> 00:06:03.792
They must use their powers

00:06:04.125 --> 00:06:07.125
and should try to change the whole world.

00:06:07.500 --> 00:06:08.375
That's My desire. I don't know

00:06:08.792 --> 00:06:11.375
in My lifetime I'll achieve it or not.

00:06:11.792 --> 00:06:13.875
But you all should decide that way

00:06:14.166 --> 00:06:17.041
and I am sure it will all work out.

00:06:17.041 --> 00:06:20.792
May God bless you. Thank you very much.

00:06:21.166 --> 00:06:21.792
Thank you very much.

